t. You need be more alert next time.（听到这"},{"type":"text","text":"个消息我很抱歉。你下次要更加警觉。）"}]},{"number":2123,"blocks":[{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：I am always on guard on the bus, because there are many thieves."},{"type":"text","text":"（因为小偷很多，所以我在公交车上总是很警惕。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：We should learn to protect ourselves. （我们应该学会保护自"},{"type":"text","text":"己。）"}]}]}